  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Please read this Privacy Policy carefully Your use of and/or registration with reddit will constitute your agreement to our policy If you cannot agree to the terms and conditions set forth below please do not use our services Additionally our Privacy Policy is part of our User Agreement and by using reddit you agree to both</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

