<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#864b50a84ebb41d58726165:Manual">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Manual"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">864b50a84ebb41d58726165</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Post Comment and Messaging Data The posts and comments you make on reddit are not private even if made to a subreddit not readily accessible to the public This means that by default they are not deleted from our servers ever and will still be accessible after your account is deleted However we only save the most recent version of comments and posts so your previous edits once overwritten are no longer available</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

