  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">how we use or disclose collected information our use of your information is limited to improving your experience It takes a lot of work to keep our site running and prevent abuse and we sometimes use your data in order to facilitate this Your information is used internally only where necessary to provide our services For instance we keep IP addresses for 90 days in order to investigate issues with our site track and block suspected spammers and otherwise maintain the integrity of the community</evidence>
